column5: Don't see 'em this big too often... not in Ontario anyways. Just 1.2 pounds shy of a record. A "HUGE" one through the ice captured on a short video.https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3bNYztT4I7Q Cool catch for me. So stoked! Bunk
That one there will stink up the frying pan,good eater.
Very cool. Congratulations and thanks for sharing.
Nice fish, certainly unusual size, have never seen one that large. Bill
Quote: Originally Posted by Bill KrejcaNice fish, certainly unusual size, have never seen one that large.BillNice fish.
Thanks fellas! Still giggling about that fish... and saying "huge" over-and-over in my head. lol.
